snippet: The State Assembly passed a bill that would give those losing their Medicaid coverage three more months to sign up for private plans.
abstract: Wisconsin State Assembly passes bill that will give those losing their Medicaid coverage three more months to sign up for private plans through the new federal online marketplace.
